{"tid":2303511,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★由Trump親自委任的上訴法官指：“看不到選舉不公的具體指控及證據，認為指控毫無根據。”","createTime":"2020-11-28T04:29:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T09:45:01.000Z","uid":19454,"like":12,"dislike":67,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"29333670bc53750ba0f2dad8dccc465c927f3696","tid":2303511,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T04:29:48.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普團隊企圖推翻總統大選結果的行動再遇挫折。有關選舉舞弊的指控再次被法庭駁回。  <br />\n<br />\n特朗普團隊之前曾要求地方法院頒令，停止賓夕法尼亞州官員確認選舉結果，但被法院拒絕。  <br />\n<br />\n特朗普一方隨即向費城的聯邦第三巡迴上訴法院提出上訴，周五也被上訴庭三名法官駁回。  其中一名上訴法官、由特朗普本人親自委任的比巴斯在判詞中指，自由及公正選舉是美國民主的命脈，選舉不公的指控很嚴重，但法庭卻看不到具體指控及證據，認為指控毫無根據。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n特朗普團隊表示，會上訴至最高法院。目前最高法院九名法官中，有六人是保守派人士。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/world/5fc168e234b031e2177bd98f/特朗普團隊圖推翻大選結果遇挫折-選舉舞弊指控再被駁回\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fworld%2F5fc168e234b031e2177bd98f%2F%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E5%9C%98%E9%9A%8A%E5%9C%96%E6%8E%A8%E7%BF%BB%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%B8%E7%B5%90%E6%9E%9C%E9%81%87%E6%8C%AB%E6%8A%98-%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E8%88%9E%E5%BC%8A%E6%8C%87%E6%8E%A7%E5%86%8D%E8%A2%AB%E9%A7%81%E5%9B%9E&d=xEw7bVcEuEkne8wYN5Y7CqooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=21af9535\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/world/5fc168e234b031e2177bd98f/特朗普團隊圖推翻大選結果遇挫折-選舉舞弊指控再被駁回</a>"},{"pid":"559071e6628f81769c1a4d293ad8dabfce9ff433","tid":2303511,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T04:29:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc9acf2e698b7415386493eac6efdba07e6a8ea1","tid":2303511,"uid":78519,"like":48,"dislike":1,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T04:31:13.000Z","msg":"TVB拉<img src=\"/assets/face