 and then proof. We have neither here</strong></ins>.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n判詞全文:<br />\n<a href=\"https://electionlawblog.org/wp-content/uploads/3rd-trump.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Felectionlawblog.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F3rd-trump.pdf&d=xEw7bVcEuEkne8wYN5Y7CqooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=75aca758\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://electionlawblog.org/wp-content/uploads/3rd-trump.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"ce5bba264846bce6e921c5bfef3d378ea08f8ef4","tid":2303511,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T04:36:04.000Z","msg":"正常上硬SC地方唔重要"},{"pid":"17bc4dcdd9021b57b54ffdd997ab44cf010c385a","tid":2303511,"uid":21545,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T04:36:35.000Z","msg":"費城的聯邦第三巡迴上訴法院<br />\n<br />\n又係廢城<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7de908e1bdebc67ccbbe5e0cd2abb86601ab926c","tid":2303511,"uid":200280,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T04:40:27.000Z","msg":"&quot;The Campaign tries to repackage these state-law claims as unconstitutional discrimination. <strong><ins>Yet its allegations are vague and conclusory</ins></strong>.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Nor does the Campaign deserve an injunction to undo Pennsylvania&rsquo;s certification of its votes. <ins><strong>The Campaign&rsquo;s claims have no merit</strong></ins>.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n判詞全文:<br />\n<a href=\"https://electionlawblog.org/wp-content/uploads/3rd-trump.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Felectionlawblog.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F3rd-trump.pdf&d=xEw7bVcEuEkne8wYN5Y7CqooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=75aca758\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://electionlawblog.org/wp-content/uploads/3rd-trump.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"34521de1f232070c042fad976be2cceacc67769a","tid":2303511,"uid":73310,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T04:43:05.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x